{"tid":1815281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Lihkg一致多謝眾勇武、和理非手足係抗爭嘅付出","createTime":"2020-01-07T11:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T16:59:48.000Z","uid":137109,"like":218,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"c73227b0a9667028c9bf671da35423508dd83ddd","tid":1815281,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:43:56.000Z","msg":"我哋唔係雞蛋，係雪球<br />\n<br />\n以往我哋用理念、手足嘅痛苦凝聚到二百萬人一齊上街<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">今後亦會Connect更多人同行，令手足嘅犧牲同失去自由變得有價值</span></strong></span><br />\n還一個更好嘅香港比下一代，再唔洗晒暑假、sem break、lunch hour同黑警、政權浴血奮戰。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔好再諗運動會唔會降溫，就算冇警暴畫面，事實證明真香港人永遠企係抗爭一方，對抗扭曲人性嘅政權。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋唔係雞蛋，係雪球，只會越來越強大，<br />\n由共同價值觀、目標支撐，彼此分擔痛苦，一齊奮鬥。</span></strong></span><br />\nUnited we stand, divided we fall<br />\n<br />\n和勇不分，每個人可以嘅話行前多步，加埋香港人嘅創意<br />\n可以掀起一場時代革命，真正光復香港。<br />\n<br />\nPS 利用呢場抗爭、破壞互信嘅人，你嘅下場會比林奠黑警更仆街"},{"pid":"7ece943cd94db4b0fe3ce429b6380c84ba1c78e2","tid":1815281,"uid":174207,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"白兵：勇武手足因為pepe頭、區選後民心散渙、風向全錯、捉鬼行動，決定唔會再出黎行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808064</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ab0ad396763dd01b67f9fafbf930361a847e769","tid":1815281,"uid":44856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"985cd16a6a5e2b240768fae05af15cc8eae6e23a","tid":1815281,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e64369b5e5ebc952f736f14428c5f967e1b5c69","tid":1815281,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69dc764a7b8f0bd41db59cabc288934c1379a2