n<br />\n以往我哋用理念、手足嘅痛苦凝聚到二百萬人一齊上街<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">今後亦會Connect更多人同行，令手足嘅犧牲同失去自由變得有價值</span></strong></span><br />\n還一個更好嘅香港比下一代，再唔洗晒暑假、sem break、lunch hour同黑警、政權浴血奮戰。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔好再諗運動會唔會降溫，就算冇警暴畫面，事實證明真香港人永遠企係抗爭一方，對抗扭曲人性嘅政權。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋唔係雞蛋，係雪球，只會越來越強大，<br />\n由共同價值觀、目標支撐，彼此分擔痛苦，一齊奮鬥。</span></strong></span><br />\nUnited we stand, divided we fall<br />\n<br />\n和勇不分，每個人可以嘅話行前多步，加埋香港人嘅創意<br />\n可以掀起一場時代革命，真正光復香港。<br />\n<br />\nPS 利用呢場抗爭、破壞互信嘅人，你嘅下場會比林奠黑警更仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n不放棄"},{"pid":"051aba69f4efa5b7d2e4a7440b2e73b6c48819d7","tid":1815281,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2408c6dae7b6c44473ab3af1595c79ff572c07a7","tid":1815281,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd997fabd0e285bcfd43d705c2c9b19140bfe965","tid":1815281,"uid":282445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"正能量<br />\n推唔到都要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd2d26bfbf5a09a5d385e595dac47d26857b28b","tid":1815281,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋係英雄"},{"pid":"4033138a42e9f4206e9f4c9c82146cd3a0b57204","tid":1815281,"uid":127454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"推 要團結向前 唔好再犯呢d錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f852d19b9e311703ee4fd6f3225ac7655ca7fac3","tid":1815281,"uid":40904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:57:09.000Z","msg":"呢排我地呢邊好多負面消息，例如：濫捕、小隊解散、捉鬼咁⋯<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記遊行嘅目的<br />\n遊行完-&gt;定死線-&gt;開花/勇武<br />\n點解由2019年6月走到今日，就算勇武點做，都會有大家支持<br />\n因為有文宣同遊行幫勇武正名，所以文宣同遊行一定會繼續搞，跟住繼續街頭抗爭，和勇不分！<br />\n<br />\n真係要毋忘初心，好多已逝去、被捕、離港手足嘅路等我地走埋落走！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n未竟全功，永不言退"},{"pid":"29bd8bb27097181ec1121c11c0ddb41b04e269da","tid":1815281,"uid":253952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcce261c4139e212323799a506a84222160529d","tid":1815281,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:58:47.000Z","msg":"多謝所有勇武 和理非<br />\n無大家既團結運動唔可以行到今日<br />\n我地唔可以俾任何野分化<br />\n分化就玩完 對唔住所有犧牲手足<br />\n一齊繼續堅持<br />\n堅持先有希望"},{"pid":"7199cb9190873cf7df906847608d87a85ab8d1c2","tid":1815281,"uid":137109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19cbf8e863a0db5cb2aef2807bc0dc50ce24daac","tid":1815281,"uid":192217,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"其實客觀既道理就係咁簡單，但人性真性真係會破壞一齊，本身將人分為勇武同和理非，就係分化，好聽啲就話分工合作，唔好聽就係話大家付出有分別<br />\n但回想初心，大家總算同路人，咁又何必分得那麼多，多包容，互相體量鼓勵，繼續行落去，好嗎？<br />\n結果如何，大家亦唔會預知，盡力做到無悔無恨便可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"和／勇無褒貶高下之分；和理非都可以好勇<br />\n勇武除gear都可以係和理非<br />\n總之都係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb5c88388e7e1363282e5a2bac0e6fb1023a4c7","tid":1815281,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b543da03ad99d7f06d96b023f3a86a99fb8c7a81","tid":1815281,"uid":256105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB